军事行动中俘虏了一些以色列人。 对于本周国际油价大跌的主要原因，光大期货研究所能源化工部研究总监钟美燕在接受《每日经济新闻》记者采访时指出，从油价的下跌驱动来看是多重利空消息的集中影响，主要体现在宏观以及地缘两个维度。谈及中东局势的突然升级，钟美燕指出，（投资者应）关注最终大国关系当中美沙、美伊、巴以走向，（这在）短期也将对油价形成一定的‘托底’效应。」全球市场屏息凝神！国际油价单周重挫近 10% 、现货黄金日线「九连阴」下，巴以爆发新一轮大规模冲突将如何影响大宗商品?"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-55e0d435a5ec7c72ff9eff186a0e9616_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.4 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625206965"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpKGKoerXzNweEAMaCTEwMTIxNDExOSCd+4qpBjAAOHxAJ3IJNjI1MjA2OTY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1696925455.298383", "card_id": "Q_620616140", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大家谈恋爱时，是更看重「对方的家庭氛围」还是「对方这个人」呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.4 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/620616140"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpKGKoerXzNweEAMaCTEwMDE5NDQwOCCJvNunBjAAOGVAKHIJNjIwNjE2MTQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1696925455.298859", "card_id": "Q_373811828", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 AI 算法工程师要求 C++?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我看了一些算法工程师要求 Java 和 C++，目前的工作大多都是 Python，为什么要求呢，实际工作中会在哪方面用到？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f1162b491e8fc8d8ccc33ac7c5593f8d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.4 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/373811828"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpKGKoerXzNweEAMaCD